### Register employee
POST http://localhost:5000/api/employees/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@company.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "employeeId": "EMP001",
  "department": "IT",
  "designation": "Software Engineer",
  "salary": 5000
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/employees/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@company.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Submit leave request
POST http://localhost:5000/api/leaves/request
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leaveType": "casual",
  "startDate": "2026-04-20",
  "endDate": "2026-04-22",
  "reason": "Family event"
}

### Get my leave requests
GET http://localhost:5000/api/leaves/my-requests
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get my remaining leave
GET http://localhost:5000/api/leaves/remaining
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Admin: get pending leave requests
GET http://localhost:5000/api/leaves/all?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Admin: approve leave
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/leaves/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Admin: reject leave
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/leaves/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rejectionReason": "Project deadline conflict"
}

### Admin: leave summary
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/leave-summary
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Employee: monthly payroll (current user)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/payroll/my-monthly?year=2026&month=4
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Admin: monthly payroll summary
GET http://localhost:5000/api/payroll/monthly-summary?year=2026&month=4
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Admin: one employee monthly payroll
GET http://localhost:5000/api/payroll/employee/1?year=2026&month=4
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
